18:22.530 --> 18:24.122
Del is on the board.

18:24.170 --> 18:25.899
Couple years ago you had
a conversation about him

18:25.930 --> 18:28.262
with another board member.
We wanted to ask you about it.

18:28.300 --> 18:31.269
You talked to Bonnie Kemp.

18:31.310 --> 18:32.834
That was all a mistake.

18:32.870 --> 18:34.337
Del and I are friends now.

18:34.380 --> 18:36.439
She gave the impression
that, at the time,

18:36.480 --> 18:38.300
you thought it was harassment.

18:38.350 --> 18:40.773
Del had just
joined the foundation.

18:40.820 --> 18:42.879
Part of my job was
to get him situated.

18:42.920 --> 18:45.241
There were a couple of...
incidents.

18:45.290 --> 18:46.780
Incidents?

18:46.820 --> 18:48.856
He invited me
to his beach house.

18:48.890 --> 18:50.858
He said I could bring
Jesse and we should

18:50.890 --> 18:52.357
bring our bathing suits.

18:52.390 --> 18:54.722
A few weeks later
he asked again.

18:54.760 --> 18:56.421
I mentioned it to Bonnie
and he apologized

18:56.460 --> 18:58.325
and backed off
the very next day.

18:58.370 --> 19:01.237
It's nothing against him.
He just wasn't my type.

19:01.270 --> 19:04.433
Type is important,
especially to a man like Gruner.

19:04.470 --> 19:07.303
Whatever it is
that you think Del did,

19:07.340 --> 19:08.432
you're wrong.

19:08.480 --> 19:10.345
He's a sweet guy.

19:10.380 --> 19:11.642
He's been very good to me.

19:11.680 --> 19:13.944
Good? How?
Well, in addition

19:13.980 --> 19:15.811
to his work with
the Hearth and Home Foundation,

19:15.850 --> 19:17.488
he funds a scholarship
at a private school

19:17.520 --> 19:19.385
in the city.
Jesse was the recipient

19:19.420 --> 19:21.251
two years ago.

19:21.290 --> 19:24.782
Without Del, I don't know
where I'd be today.

19:24.830 --> 19:27.799
Well, what do you think?

19:27.830 --> 19:30.367
I think she doesn't fit
our victim profile.

19:30.400 --> 19:32.698
She's older than the others.
She's taller, fair-haired.

19:32.730 --> 19:33.958
The most striking
difference, of course,

19:34.000 --> 19:35.661
is that she's still alive.

19:35.700 --> 19:38.260
_ If Gruner wasn't _
stalking her, what was he d0ing?

19:38.310 --> 19:40.574
Like many serial killers,
Gruner's a narcissist.

19:40.610 --> 19:43.374
He saw Tabitha Laird and her son
and he saw an opportunity

19:43.410 --> 19:45.640
to bask in the glory
of his own good deeds.

19:45.680 --> 19:47.648
He doesn't contribute to
charities or fund scholarships

19:47.680 --> 19:49.648
because he's a good person;
he does it 'cause he likes

19:49.680 --> 19:51.841
the attention that he gets.
You said you were looking

19:51.890 --> 19:54.450
into other areas of his life.
I say we cut our losses,

19:54.490 --> 19:55.855
compare whatever else
you've learned with our list

19:55.890 --> 19:57.482
of potential victims, and then

19:57.530 --> 20:00.658
_ see if we can
find a connection.

20:00.700 --> 20:03.589
You gonna tell me why
you asked me to meet you here,

20:03.630 --> 20:05.621
or do I have to guess?

20:08.700 --> 20:11.828
Latif.
He came here straight
from the hospital.

20:11.870 --> 20:15.374
You were wrong about
the pederast Hodge.

20:15.410 --> 20:18.675
The boy's true abductor was
a woman named Baraa Nezain.

20:18.710 --> 20:20.371
Until a few hours
ago, she resided

20:20.420 --> 20:22.945
in the same building
as the Malak family.

20:22.980 --> 20:26.609
She lost her own son
to leukemia in 2012.

20:26.650 --> 20:28.686
Latif was to be the replacement.

20:28.720 --> 20:30.779
She lured him to her
flat, she drugged him,

20:30.830 --> 20:33.321
and she hid him there.
Then she put his backpack

20:33.360 --> 20:35.624
in that alleyway to mislead
the police as to when and where

20:35.660 --> 20:38.663
he was taken_. Just
as you predicted.

20:40.970 --> 20:42.437
He's going
home tonight.

20:42.470 --> 20:43.960
'Cause of you.

20:46.570 --> 20:49.368
No, I thought it was Hodge.
I was positive.

20:49.410 --> 20:51.344
You wished it
to be Hodge.

20:51.380 --> 20:52.642
That's understandable.

20:52.680 --> 20:54.409
You were drawn to this
case because you also

20:54.450 --> 20:56.338
fell victim to a
sexual predator.

20:58.390 --> 21:00.415
I'm sorry. I've known
since our second meeting.

21:00.460 --> 21:03.725
If you are to hone your
skills as an investigator,

21:03.760 --> 21:06.524
you really must know
your blind spots.

21:08.530 --> 21:10.361
How did you take
everything that I told you

21:10.400 --> 21:11.992
and come up with this?

21:12.030 --> 21:14.999
All in good time, Ms. Winter.

21:15.040 --> 21:18.464
Firstly, I've got an offer
