for more kids in 2014

22:03.790 --> 22:06.543
than in any prior year
of our history.

22:10.560 --> 22:13.529
To talk about what lies ahead,
here is a man

22:13.560 --> 22:16.996
whose generosity
with his money and his time

22:17.030 --> 22:21.467
truly embodies the spirit
of Hearth and Home.

22:21.500 --> 22:23.502
Del Gruner.

22:23.540 --> 22:25.838
Thank you, Warren.
Thank you.

22:30.850 --> 22:34.377
So, this rich guy dies,
and he finds himself

22:34.420 --> 22:37.583
in front of St. Peter
at the Pearly Gates...

22:40.860 --> 22:43.579
I had no idea you were involved
with the foundation.

22:43.630 --> 22:44.779
I wasn't.

22:44.830 --> 22:46.559
But then I saw you'd
be here tonight,

22:46.590 --> 22:47.955
and all of a sudden,
I knew how I wanted to spend

22:48.000 --> 22:49.922
my severance
check from Leda.

22:49.960 --> 22:53.566
Hmm. Well, if you're planning
on making a scene, be my guest.

22:53.600 --> 22:55.136
Just don't expect it
to do any good.

22:56.970 --> 22:59.962
It'll only take a few seconds
for you to be removed.

23:00.010 --> 23:01.898
I'm not here
to make a scene, Del.

23:01.940 --> 23:04.408
I just wanted to tell you
to enjoy it all while it lasts.

23:04.450 --> 23:06.873
(chuckles) And what makes you
think it's not going to last?

23:06.910 --> 23:09.413
Carrie Morse, Stacey Goff,

23:09.450 --> 23:11.680
Vivian Russell--
we know about them.

23:11.720 --> 23:12.982
It's only a matter of time
before we

23:13.960 --> 23:15.484
I'm sorry.

23:15.520 --> 23:17.078
None of those names
ring a bell. Should they?

23:17.120 --> 23:18.451
TABITHA:
Miss Watson.

23:18.490 --> 23:20.754
What are you doing here?

23:20.800 --> 23:22.893
Ms. Laird. Well, Del and I
used to work together.

23:22.930 --> 23:25.125
I saw the foundation_was
hosting an event tonight,

23:25.170 --> 23:26.899
and I thought I'd come
