23:30.670 --> 23:32.137
We had a very interesting
conversation.

23:32.170 --> 23:33.603
Actually, we didn't.

23:33.640 --> 23:36.108
Um, they thought you
and I had a problem.

23:36.140 --> 23:38.449
I told them they
couldn't be more wrong.

23:38.480 --> 23:40.471
